<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cadastro</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #0f0f0f;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .card {
      background-color: #1a1a1a;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 420px;
      border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
    }

    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .logo h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .logo span {
      color: #4f46e5;
    }

    .logo p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }

    .input-group {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    label {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #aaa;
    }

    input {
      padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
      background-color: #242424;
      border: 1px solid #333;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #fff;
      outline: none;
      transition: border 0.2s;
    }

    input:focus {
      border-color: #4f46e5;
    }

    input::placeholder {
      color: #555;
    }

    button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.85rem;
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #4338ca;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #555;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="logo">
      <h1>IMC <span>Pro</span></h1>
      <p>Crie sua conta para começar</p>
    </div>

    <form action="/cadastro" method="POST">
      <div class="input-group">
        <label>Nome completo</label>
        <input type="text" name="nome" placeholder="Nome" required>
      </div>

      <div class="input-group">
        <label>Email</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" required>
      </div>

      <div class="input-group">
        <label>Senha</label>
        <input type="password" name="senha" placeholder="••••••••" required>
      </div>

      <button type="submit">Criar conta</button>
    </form>

    <div class="footer">
      Ao cadastrar você concorda com os termos de uso
    </div>
    <p style="text-align:center; margin-top:1rem; color:#94a3b8; font-size:0.85rem;">
  Já tem conta? <a href="/login" style="color:#f43f5e;">Entrar</a>
</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>